20200610 Hilt設定
REF: https://developer.android.com/training/dependency-injection/hilt-android?authuser=1
1. build.gradle(Project)新增buildscript{} **必須至於最頂層
2. 修改buildscript內容，新增版本及dependencies，新增plugin
3. build.gradle(Module) dependencies新增依賴項，plugin{}新增id
4. 新增App class繼承Application()，加入@HiltAndroidApp宣告
5. AndroidManifest application{}新增android:name=".App"屬性
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
